# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Public env vars (SvelteKit PUBLIC_ prefix → exposed to the browser bundle).
# Copy to `.env` and fill in. Client IDs are NOT secret; never put a real secret
# behind a PUBLIC_ name.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Google OAuth client ID for Drive sync. Create one with the one-time steps in
# docs/setup-google-drive.md, then paste it here. Leave BLANK to run the app
# local-only (sync disabled, no Google sign-in).
PUBLIC_GOOGLE_OAUTH_CLIENT_ID=
